body.paragraph:
Saṅkhārakkhandhaṃ ṭhapetvā avasesā saṅkhārā 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='231', original='avasesā saṅkhārā saṅkhārā (syā.)', type='auto', previous='Saṅkhārakkhandhaṃ ṭhapetvā avasesā saṅkhārā '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='avasesā saṅkhārā'}
	Alternative{lang='syā.', text='avasesā saṅkhārā saṅkhārā'}}
, na saṅkhārakkhandho. Saṅkhārakkhandho saṅkhārā ceva saṅkhārakkhandho ca.

Avasesā khandhāavasesā khandhā khandhā 
Note { id=1, line='12', referenceLine='255', original='avasesā khandhā khandhā (syā.) evamuparipi', type='auto', previous='Avasesā khandhā '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='khandhā'}
	Alternative{lang='syā.', text='avasesā khandhā khandhā'}}
na vedanākkhandho.

Pacchimabhavikānaṃ upapajjantānaṃ 
Note { id=2, line='21', referenceLine='677', original='pacchimabhavikānaṃ pañcavokāraṃ upapajjantānaṃ (sī. syā.)', type='auto', previous='Pacchimabhavikānaṃ upapajjantānaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='Pacchimabhavikānaṃ upapajjantānaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='sī. syā.', text='pacchimabhavikānaṃ pañcavokāraṃ upapajjantānaṃ'}}
tesaṃ saññākkhandho nuppajjissati, no ca tesaṃ vedanākkhandho nuppajjati. Parinibbantānaṃ tesaṃ saññākkhandho ca nuppajjissati vedanākkhandho ca nuppajjati.
